.SH "Detailed Description"
.PP 
Represents a hexagonal game board composed of cube-coordinate tiles\&. 

The \fBBoard\fP is implemented as an unordered map keyed by \fBCubeCoord\fP, enabling constant-time lookup of tiles\&. Each tile may store its owner (\fBCompany\fP) and visual color data\&. The board supports neighbor detection and manipulation of tile attributes\&.

.PP
The design is suitable for strategy or simulation games utilizing hex grids\&. 
